    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am writing this letter to request for a transfer to the headoffice in UK for a period of six months.",
        "In line with the company's policy of a transfer to the mainoffice after working for 5years i will love to work at the mainofficr for a different work experience and it would also be lovely for me to work directly with the big bosses and get to learn from them and also meet my other colleagues in the UK. I will also love to learn about the life and culture of the new state.",
